3. Robust Exploration Loop (12 points)\
Implement the main decision-making callback that the framework calls once per iteration. The random\
baseline ignores many edge cases that arise during real exploration. Your implementation must handle:\
\'95 Path validation: As the robot discovers new obstacles, a previously planned path may become blocked.\
Validate the remaining path each iteration using 
